    "type": 0,
    "content": "**Welcome to the AgentX Hackathon 2026!** 🎉\n\nThis is your space to connect with fellow participants, share ideas, ask each other questions, and have a good time throughout the sprint.\n\nWhether you're joining solo or with a team, from México, Colombia, or Chile — you're part of something exciting. We've got **91 teams ready to build, learn, and push the boundaries of what agentic systems can do**!\n\nA few reminders:\n\nKeep it in English so everyone can follow along\nFor technical questions directed at mentors, head over to #ask-mentors\nFor official updates and event links, follow #hackathon-announcements\n\nDon't be shy — introduce yourself, share what excites you about the challenge, and let's make this a great experience for everyone.\n\nLet's build! 🚀",
